{"tid":1872390,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"稱肺炎為美武器 內蒙漢造謠被拘","createTime":"2020-02-10T05:12:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-10T06:08:58.000Z","uid":17506,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"cb9c191732a5524b1909e5f43224aee03403bf5b","tid":1872390,"uid":17506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T05:12:00.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】上月26日，內蒙通遼市科左後旗朝魯吐鎮居民滿&times;在「快手」APP發表名為「經典話題：不聽的後悔一輩子」的短視頻，稱「現在的新型冠狀病毒引起的肺炎，是美國向中國使用病毒基因武器造成的」。該視頻在快手的播放量達到近1.4萬次。當地警介入調查後，滿&times;對自己發布虛假信息供認不諱。科左後旗公安局日前給予滿&times;行政拘留10日處罰，並罰款500元人民幣。有律師表示，在疫情防控期間，任何組織和個人製造和故意傳播謠言將可能處以10日以下拘留；構成犯罪的，將最高判處7年以下的有期徒刑。<br />\n<br />\n（人民日報）<br />\n（武漢肺炎）<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b/article/20200210/s00013/1581273689610/%e7%a8%b1%e8%82%ba%e7%82%8e%e7%82%ba%e7%be%8e%e6%ad%a6%e5%99%a8-%e5%85%a7%e8%92%99%e6%bc%a2%e9%80%a0%e8%ac%a0%e8%a2%ab%e6%8b%98\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e5%259c%258b%2Farticle%2F20200210%2Fs00013%2F1581273689610%2F%25e7%25a8%25b1%25e8%2582%25ba%25e7%2582%258e%25e7%2582%25ba%25e7%25be%258e%25e6%25ad%25a6%25e5%2599%25a8-%25e5%2585%25a7%25e8%2592%2599%25e6%25bc%25a2%25e9%2580%25a0%25e8%25ac%25a0%25e8%25a2%25ab%25e6%258b%2598&d=nNI0xXmu%2FnmsXsjxjv7MVfS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=fba0bc35\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e5%259c%258b%2Farticle%2F20200210%2Fs00013%2F1581273689610%2F%25e7%25a8%25b1%25e8%2582%25ba%25e7%2582%258e%25e7%2582%25ba%25e7%25be%258e%25e6%25ad%25a6%25e5%2599%25a8-%25e5%2585%25a7%25e8%2592%2599%25e6%25bc%25a2%25e9%2580%25a0%25e8%25ac%25a0%25e8%25a2%25ab%25e6%258b%2598&h=727e7563\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b/article/20200210/s00013/1581273689610/%e7%a8%b1%e8%82%ba%e7%82%8e%e7%82%ba%e7%be%8e%e6%ad%a6%e5%99%a8-%e5%85%a7%e8%92%99%e6%bc%a2%e9%80%a0%e8%ac%a0%e8%a2%ab%e6%8b%98</a>"},{"pid":"090d796b97a5b078